  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380630/extras/42efcc8ad3ea12796fe6e06d5576e45c.webp?t=1707155658\" width=600 height=44 /></span><br><br>The Adventures of Wolf and Hood - A Jigsaw Tale is a wonderfully original fairy tale story told through 20 beautiful hand illustrated jigsaw puzzles.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380630/extras/04ee15405e4b6e640227cd77fd9b1d44.poster.avif?t=1707155658\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380630/extras/04ee15405e4b6e640227cd77fd9b1d44.webm?t=1707155658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380630/extras/04ee15405e4b6e640227cd77fd9b1d44.mp4?t=1707155658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380630/extras/f2bfcc54156e7aea4b2223d27e28fe44.webp?t=1707155658\" width=600 height=44 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Follow familiar fairy tale characters in a brand new adventure<br></li><li> Choose from six different puzzle sizes, from 24 to 294 pieces<br></li><li> Progress is saved automatically so you can come back to a puzzle later<br></li><li> Take your time to admire the completed scenes and zoom in on the details<br></li><li> Subtle animated elements bring the scenes to life as you play <br></li><li> The most realistic looking puzzle pieces found in any jigsaw puzzle game<br></li><li> Very satisfying sound effects recorded from real jigsaw puzzles for an authentic experience<br></li><li> Read the whole completed story in Gallery Mode, like a real picture book</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video 